- Set up proper development tools
- Configure TypeScript properly
- Use proper debugging tools
- Implement proper testing environment

## Extension Features
- Implement proper commands
- Use proper VSCode UI components
- Implement proper configuration
- Handle proper extension lifecycle

## Testing
- Write unit tests for functionality
- Test across different VSCode versions
- Implement proper testing environment
- Use VSCode testing tools

## Publishing
- Follow VSCode marketplace guidelines
- Implement proper versioning
- Create proper documentation
- Handle proper updates

## Performance
